struct.exostring: Initiates with the player the second time they exit the ebon hawk, if the player has not yet paid the fee.
Selected by the player AFTER player has paid the fee

Initates with the player when they first exit the ebon hawk
This is the customs official in the landing area just outside the ebon hawk. Like on Kashyyyk, he will not let the player disembark without paying the landing fee. Player can persuade his way out of it, though.
Moves a short ways back after initiating dialogue, but always stays in the bay.
Player is forced back aboard the ebon hawk
Player does not already have the star map
